{"about_the_game":"Even in defeat, the Gahars never truly die. They retreat into darkness and bide their time until the opportunity to arise again is upon them...<br><br>Morbid: The Lords of Ire is a continuation and reinvention of the critically acclaimed isometric Souls-like ARPG \u201cMorbid: The Seven Acolytes\u201d with the heroic Striver returning once more to do battle with horrific creatures in a dark and twisted world of pain and suffering.<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2171560/extras/Adventure.png?t=1716972671\" /><br><br>Take on gruesome foes in an all-new 3D perspective. Slaughter hideous creatures using a range of vicious weapons, equipment and blessings to eviscerate everything in your path.<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2171560/extras/GIF-New1.gif?t=1716972671\" /><br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2171560/extras/Sanity.png?t=1716972671\" /><br><br>Building on the sanity system from Morbid: The Seven Acolytes, how you approach combat can have a dramatic impact on the world around you. Succumbing to insanity can grant incredible power, but at great personal risk, and will dynamically change how you perceive the world around you.<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2171560/extras/Store_GIF_2_Sanity__1_.gif?t=1716972671\" /><br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2171560/extras/Landscapes.png?t=1716972671\" /><br><br>Battle your way through the five lands of Ire - horrific realms populated by five unique factions, from wintry mountains to rotten cities and beyond. Fulfill your sacred duty to rid the lands of the evil that has befallen them.<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2171560/extras/Store_GIF_3_TorturedLandscapes__1_.gif?t=1716972671\" /><br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2171560/extras/Test_1.png?t=1716972671\" /><br><br>Cut down everything standing in your way to take on the five fearsome Lords of Ire, up the challenge by seeking out uniquely monstrous dark &amp; powerful creatures, lurking in each level.<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2171560/extras/Store_GIF_4_VileMonsters__1_.gif?t=1716972671\" /><br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2171560/extras/Features.png?t=1716972671\" /><br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Explore diverse environments across five unique lands filled with nightmarish visions and stomach-churning creatures.<br></li><li>Experiment with different playstyles using a variety of weapon styles, runes &amp; blessings<br></li><li>Fight to preserve your sanity, or succumb to the madness and harness it\u2026<br></li><li>Test your skills against horrific enemies, dark monstrosities and epic boss battles with the mighty Lords of Ire.<br></li><li>Fully realise the horrors of Morbid as the series steps into a new 3D perspective.</li></ul>","achievements":{"highlighted":[{"name":"Reach The Sanctuary","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2171560/88b1f20a5037fdb0dea10249da3a1894c5f8ca44.jpg"},{"name":"Discover the Cursed Mountains","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2171560/96aa2cea6f4167eca849b169d69c4f37b0bdd288.jpg"},{"name":"Discover the Rotten City","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2171560/a0bcd69db07785d608e1129d888a5f53315fa208.jpg"},{"name":"Discover the Ancient Crater","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2171560/7b45c32861586765e